 with the expansion, and i pray that I see the phrase &quot;can someone with lockpicks open this door for me?&quot; alot more often.....and for your info, Locksmiths in RL make a killing letting people in their cars, houses, etc... just remember to charge alot of money for this service:) <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#3B3B3B><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub2.ezboard.com/uhoophalflingsbane.showPublicProfile>Hoop Halflingsbane</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Global user</span><br> <font color=#FF0000>(1/21/00 9:53:55 am)</font><br>    </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: ...only a rogue could appreciate this (or a locksmith)</span><hr size=1> Yeah, lockpicking is the only thing I've ever been ask for (a whopping 2 times now).  Both regarded the Bank door in Freeport. <p>Hoop Halflingsbane, Mithaniel Marr<BR>
